#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(void)
{
	long long int t,a,kk=0,n,bb=1;
	scanf("%lld",&t);
	while(t--)
	{
		long long int count=0;
		kk=0;
		for(long long int i=0;i<15;i++)
		{
			scanf("%lld",&a);
			kk=kk^a;
		}
		scanf("%lld",&n);
		while(kk>0)
		{
			if((kk&bb)==1)
			{
				count=count+1;
			}
			kk=kk>>1;
		}
		if(count>n)
		{
			printf("YES\n");
		}
		else{
			printf("NO\n");
		}
	}
	return 0;
}
